       const edgePage = 'price-quotes-and-free-recommendations';
       let isEdgeCategory = false;
       (function() {
         var d = document,
           s = 'script';
         if(window.location.pathname.includes(edgePage)) {
           for (let edgeCategory of edgeCategories) {
             if (window.location.pathname.includes(edgeCategory)) {
               isEdgeCategory = true;
               break;
             }
           }
         }

           }

          Have questions?
         </h2>
         <div _ngcontent-sc75="" class="faq-list">
          <!-- -->
          <dl _ngcontent-sc75="" class="faqs">
           <dt _ngcontent-sc75="" class="faq-question">
            <p _ngcontent-sc75="" class="strong">
             Are you trying to sell me something?
            </p>
           </dt>
           <dd _ngcontent-sc75="" class="faq-answer">
            <p _ngcontent-sc75="">
             Never! We donât sell products and weâll never push you into buying anything. Our only goal is to help connect you with relevant software options. What you purchase (or not) is up to you.
            </p>
           </dd>
          </dl>
          <dl _ngcontent-sc75="" class="faqs">
           <dt _ngcontent-sc75="" class="faq-question">

            </p>

           <dd _ngcontent-sc75="" class="faq-answer">
            <p _ngcontent-sc75="">

            </p>
           </dd>
          </dl>
          <dl _ngcontent-sc75="" class="faqs">
           <dt _ngcontent-sc75="" class="faq-question">

            <p _ngcontent-sc75="">
             Our team of advisors is based out of Austin, Texas. Theyâre friends, coworkers, siblings, parents, dog owners, music listeners, park goers, beer lovers and software selection specialists! Our software selection advisors specialize in certain industries, including construction, retail, medical and more, which means youâll always be paired up with someone who knows your market. Our advisors love helping business like yours thrive!
            </p>
           </dd>
          </dl>
          <dl _ngcontent-sc75="" class="faqs">
           <dt _ngcontent-sc75="" class="faq-question">

             Will l get spammed with phone calls?

             Weâll reach out to connect, but weâre definitely not here to spam you. If youâd prefer a specific time to connect, weâve made it easy to book a call on your schedule. Pick when works best for you.
            </p>

          </dl>
